The following preprint is now available on arXiv,
http://arxiv.org/abs/1005.4236

A. Kock and J. Kock: Local fibered right adjoints are polynomial

Abstract: For any locally cartesian closed category E, we prove that a
local fibered
right adjoint between slices of E is given by a polynomial. The slices in
question are taken in a well known fibered sense.


